changelog.comment: Initial entry. Reviewer 1 checked entry for correctness, changed enzyme and reaction description

Fixed typo in enzyme name (Vhal -> VhaA). Reviewer 1 checked for correctness, add reference  (doi.org/10.1039/C4OB00474D), change evidence from 'Knock-out studies' to 'Chemical probe', and remove reference (doi:10.1186/1471-2164-15-363) from evidence section.
Added cofactor information. Fixed reaction SMARTS indexing.

reactions.description: Chlorinates bht 2 and bht 6 of vancomycin. The bond to the PCP domain of module 2 of the vancomycin NRPS might be important for the reaction. There is no study on the substrate specificity for the second chlorination reaction in vancomycin biosynthesis on bht 6 so far.
